org.eclipse.nvplayout.model

Class MemoryConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.nvplayout.model.MemoryConfiguration

  • public class MemoryConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    MemoryConfiguration is the model for the global memory configuration view.
    This model contain the global configuration, i-e :
    • The Application Name.
    • The Calibration Start Address.
    • The RAM shadow Start Address.
    • The ROM Start Address.
    • The Eeprom Alias Start Address.
    • The Calibration Version (Major, Minor and Subversion).
    • The different size of memory sector (Calibration).

    Based on a MVC model

    Version:
    0.0 Alpha EarlyAccess Beta Tester
    Author:
    GLI feat Software Team
